{"tid":2114721,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"求救(有圖) 每朝訓醒屙尿都會屙到周圍係 好辛苦","createTime":"2020-07-19T04:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T06:25:30.000Z","uid":181257,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cafe8790a06e7db4801bfebad0fb704fa95ec155","tid":2114721,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:53:47.000Z","msg":"每朝訓醒屙尿個啫窿都好似黐埋咗咁<br />\n一屙尿就會有兩條屙柱射出嚟，有時三條，<br />\n<br />\n永遠無固定方向，估唔到佢會射邊一邊，搞到地下濕晒，有時個廁所板又濕<br />\n<br />\n最慘係射濕自己隻腳，有時太早唔想沖涼就會濕住再訓<br />\n到底應該點做好，我係咪有咩病<br />\n<br />\n圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaWEOkM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaWEOkM.png&h=9d878f2a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad87c3e3705873d1ffc327aae3865a4cdd7c967e","tid":2114721,"uid":50502,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTxxi7Bu_vPg4FgvFeNJDyNBl6kr2jzyqEszg&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTxxi7Bu_vPg4FgvFeNJDyNBl6kr2jzyqEszg%26usqp%3DCAU&h=443f19d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c09fa88038e3ccb2d41841e957a928cf41d4045f","tid":2114721,"uid":351574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:55:57.000Z","msg":"坐下屙"},{"pid":"d9e4af0cb1e1a810e4aae4807773c60e529cb26c","tid":2114721,"uid":181257,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ad87c3e3705873d1ffc327aae3865a4cdd7c967e","tid":2114721,"uid":50502,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcTxxi7Bu_vPg4FgvFeNJDyNBl6kr2jzyqEszg&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcTxxi7Bu_vPg4FgvFeNJDyNBl6kr2jzyqEszg%26usqp%3DCAU&h=443f19d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:5