開口處出現了臨時阻塞。舉例說，男性於自慰或性愛射精後，有小量精液殘留在尿道口，需要靠尿液沖出，再加上陰莖充血並未完全減退使尿道暫時變窄，容易導致射精後的尿流不暢順和分叉情況。更常見的情況就是，男性於晚上睡眠裏，整夜間積存了尿液於膀胱內，令膀胱內部壓力增加，到起床時上洗手間，尿液排出時自然會加大噴射力度，致使尿道口形態暫時改變才引起小便分叉。這些情況均不是病態，並會在下一回小便時回復正常。"},{"pid":"1f466896dd6f5a10249009ce55b166bee9551a40","tid":2114721,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ab8114870dc9c412ebc0102eef66b310793d0f","tid":2114721,"uid":9566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:57:53.000Z","msg":"唔識反開包皮先屙?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"割咗 個頭得番啲肉"},{"pid":"42c46986a63e7af88b902b2b663a8388d67707e0","tid":2114721,"uid":41423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:00:55.000Z","msg":"坐低疴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4999f51bd288f9a91563f760893dc98f06321b","tid":2114721,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f048ff597a4a4dc2b3dbd178f0981c16583e11f7","tid":2114721,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"用廁紙筒笠住先痾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:01:46.000Z","msg":"邊有咁多廁紙筒呀Ching <br />\n用手當筒得唔得"},{"pid":"4fc878d4baeed2e16c4803a598414aaf28d00280","tid":2114721,"uid":92002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"有粒腎石卡左係尿道中間"},{"pid":"5a98bccffc8a0816adcdca508bdc1fe4cfaec46e","tid":2114721,"uid":227971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"痾之前整一整開你龜頭個尿道口就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"969d69a318bbcf1548e73755e15b7028f9ba91d3","tid":2114721,"uid":181257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fc878d4baeed2e16c4803a598414aaf28d00280","tid":2114721,"uid":92002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"有粒腎石卡左係尿道中間"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"真定假呀清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shock